snippet: Charlie Mann scored 18 points, including the go-ahead basket with 35.8 seconds left in overtime, and Georgia beat No. 21 Missouri, 70-64, in a Southeastern Conference opener.
abstract: Georgia beats Missouri, 70-64, in Southeastern conference opener; other men's college basketball news noted.
